&quot;Raymonde de Laroche (22 August 1882 – 18 July 1919), born Elise Raymonde Deroche, was a French pilot and the first woman in the world to receive an aeroplane pilot's licence.&quot;
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymonde_de_Laroche" rel="nofollow">en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymonde_de_Laroche</a>

Another photo of her is depicted in <a href="http://chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn85042462/1909-12-19/ed-1/seq-167/" rel="nofollow">Los Angeles herald [microform]., December 19, 1909, Page 105</a>, &quot;FIRST WOMAN TO FLY ALONE, MME. DELAROCHE&quot;
